Abby Mavers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abby_Mavers 0 Abby Imogen Mavers (born 20 April 1990 in Liverpool) is an English actress. She is well known for her role as Dynasty Barry in the BBC drama series, Waterloo Road from 2013 until 2014. She is the daughter of actor Gary Mavers, who recently appeared as Gordon Livesy in Emmerdale, and the niece of musician Lee Mavers, frontman of The La's. Her Waterloo Road co star Tommy Knight was her real life boyfriend for several years. Abby_Imogen_Mavers ( born 20_April_1990 in Liverpool ) is an_English_actress .
